OL,3,CHomes evacuated in Lurgan security
OL,4,Calert
OL,6,FA number of roads have been closed in
OL,7,Fthe centre of Lurgan and homes
OL,8,Fevacuated because of a security alert.
OL,10,FDUP MP Carla Lockhart said the town
OL,11,Fhall in the County Armagh town had
OL,12,Fbeen opened for evacuated residents.
OL,14,FPolice have asked road users to avoid
OL,15,Fa number of road in the Church Place
OL,16,Farea on Tuesday. Church Place, Church
OL,17,FWalk and Wellington Street are
OL,18,Fcurrently closed to traffic, as are
OL,19,Fsections of Market Street, William
OL,20,FStreet and North Street. They've asked
OL,21,Fdrivers to seek alternative routes.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
