OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1774947927
OL,3,CHomes evacuated in Lurgan security
OL,4,Calert
OL,6,FMs Lockhart said: "I would urge
OL,7,Feveryone to follow the advice of the
OL,8,FPSNI and avoid the area.
OL,10,F"I recognise the significant
OL,11,Fdisruption this will cause to local
OL,12,Fresidents, businesses and those
OL,13,Ftravelling through the town, but these
OL,14,Fmeasures are necessary to ensure the
OL,15,Fsafety of all.
OL,17,F"I welcome the steps taken to provide
OL,18,Fsupport for those affected, including
OL,19,Fthe opening of Lurgan Town Hall for
OL,20,Fanyone who has been evacuated."
