OL,3,CHomes evacuated in Lurgan security
OL,4,Calert
OL,6,FUUP leader Jon Burrows MLA said on
OL,7,Fsocial media:
OL,9,F"This is an ongoing security alert
OL,10,Ffollowing the discovery of a
OL,11,Fsuspicious vehicle at the entrance to
OL,12,FLurgan PSNI station. This will have
OL,13,Fcaused significant distress and
OL,14,Fdisruption to local residents."
